{"tid":1477756,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想講講818！大家入黎討論下！","createTime":"2019-08-16T08:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T08:47:23.000Z","uid":214946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c16ca6efb4ba3c9ad4a5c92b3dced245f7305afa","tid":1477756,"uid":214946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"以下呢篇係李一平講解<span style=\"color: gold;\">防中共嫁禍示威者，抹黑反送中運動</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/8/15/n11456345.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F19%2F8%2F15%2Fn11456345.htm&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal7zLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=f6704fa0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/8/15/n11456345.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n專家也向港警喊話，千萬要認清局勢，這時不是維護中共的時候，而是要先保護自己，否則港警將會被率先犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n外界擔憂，中共是否會出兵香港鎮壓反送中活動。中國異議人士、加拿大華人與作家李一平在youtube自媒體「一平論政」上談到，針對香港8.18大游行，<span style=\"color: gold;\">中共已做三項惡毒安排</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">第一</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">全面鎮壓「勇武派」年輕人</span>；<span style=\"color: red;\">第二</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">殺害香港警察嫁禍反送中</span>；<span style=\"color: red;\">第三</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">公開調動武警進港</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他呼籲，香港反對派應放棄玉石俱焚心態，<span style=\"color: gold;\">採用低烈度持續抗爭策略</span>，只要<span style=\"color: gold;\">持續下去拖垮中共</span>，香港人才會獲的真正的勝利。<br />\n<br />\n針對目前香港才經歷幾波激烈警民衝突，以及被港警暴力對待的局勢，李一平分析，818大家必須要改變戰術，根據他從體制內得到消息，為鎮壓這次反送中運動，中共已做好三項安排，首先中共派遣數千名防暴警察進入香港，要與香港警察一起鎮壓勇武派年輕人，現在已有足夠的警力可以包圍攻擊勇武派年青人。<br />\n<br />\n如何面對這樣的嚴峻情勢？李一平提出三點解方。大家一定要動員更多人參加這次大遊行，現在香港警方力量雖然很大，但<span style=\"color: gold;\">還不足以阻攔百萬人的大示威遊行</span>，所以遊行人越多越好越安全。但希望大家一定要<span style=\"color: gold;\">保持非暴力原則</span>，佔領這道德制高點，就是佔領政治戰、輿論戰的制高點。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都明兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n但唔好攬炒住！唔好俾憤怒控制思想！<br />\n818 勿玉石俱焚 兄弟請小心安全 避開中共間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔可以再損失任何手足啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🇭🇰🇭🇰"},{"pid":"d69d26588a15e915b494415a53daeb92f89fd8bc","tid":1477756,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2b211a465d75c0f0814d52780a1c3e5516b31616","tid":1477756,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:37:35.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2nDsML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2nDsML.jpg&h=4c89349c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZua3j6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZua3j6.jpg&h=b4b0b5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdrQiT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdrQiT1.jpg&h=57ddf216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YvdK1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YvdK1E.jpg&h=e1c38679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D83Sf8j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD83Sf8j.jpg&h=da01072f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSeBHOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJSeBHOk.jpg&h=4d624e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7KeuxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7KeuxB.jpg&